            <title><![CDATA[Elder Scrolls 6 Should Probably Focus On Choices Over Stats, Original Oblivion Dev Says]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gamespot.com/articles/elder-scrolls-6-should-probably-focus-on-choices-over-stats-original-oblivion-dev-says/1100-6531189/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f</link>
